-- Zambian Power-Plant Fault Causes Outage Across the Copper-Producing Nation
-- Obert Simwanza
-- 2010-06-18T10:40:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/zambian-power-plant-fault-causes-outage-across-the-copper-producing-nation.html

          
          
             A fault with a circuit-breaker at
the Kariba North hydro power plant in Zambia has caused an
outage across most of the copper-producing country, Lucy Zimba,
a spokeswoman for the Zambia Electricity Supply Corp., said in
an phone interview today.  
          
          


  


        